[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation="bottom-to-top" css=".vc_custom_1447338419186{margin-top: -40px !important;}"]

LUNCH & DINNER

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1447335160267{padding-bottom: 300px !important;}"][vc_column width="1/3" css=".vc_custom_1447337282688{margin-bottom: 50px !important;border-right-width: 2px !important;border-right-color: #ffffff !important;border-right-style: dashed !important;}"][vc_single_image image="33" img_size="full" alignment="center" css_animation="left-to-right"][vc_column_text css_animation="left-to-right" css=".vc_custom_1447334945676{margin-top: -35px !important;}"]

STARTERS

[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image="34" img_size="full" alignment="center" css_animation="left-to-right" css=".vc_custom_1447334959879{margin-top: -20px !important;}"][vc_column_text css_animation="left-to-right" css=".vc_custom_1447335495674{padding-right: 55px !important;padding-left: 55px !important;}"]

BAYBERRY WINGS

Fried, then tossed in Thai honey hot sauce, with cracked black pepper bleu cheese and celery sticks. 200g.........$10.00

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation="left-to-right" css=".vc_custom_1447691860981{padding-right: 55px !important;padding-left: 55px !important;}"]

MUSAKA

The recipe calls for 'chubritsa', a Bulgarian herb that can be difficult to find in the states. 200g.........$11.00

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation="left-to-right" css=".vc_custom_1447691936368{padding-right: 55px !important;padding-left: 55px !important;}"]

KASHMIRI LAMB

Combines the area's fruits and nuts with the ingredients and the cooking style of the Moghuls. 200g.........$13.00

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation="left-to-right" css=".vc_custom_1447691996520{padding-right: 55px !important;padding-left: 55px !important;}"]

TOFU PARMIGIANA

Fried, then tossed in Thai honey hot sauce, with cracked black pepper bleu cheese and celery sticks. 200g.........$10.00

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3" css=".vc_custom_1447337287063{margin-bottom: 50px !important;border-right-width: 2px !important;border-right-color: #ffffff !important;border-right-style: dashed !important;}"][vc_single_image image="33" img_size="full" alignment="center" css_animation="bottom-to-top"][vc_column_text css_animation="bottom-to-top" css=".vc_custom_1447335821654{margin-top: -35px !important;}"]

MAIN DISHES

[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image="34" img_size="full" alignment="center" css_animation="bottom-to-top" css=".vc_custom_1447335765628{margin-top: -20px !important;}"][vc_column_text css_animation="bottom-to-top" css=".vc_custom_1447764935579{padding-right: 55px !important;padding-left: 55px !important;}"]

GROUND BEEF

These are beef filled tortilla shells baked in a creamy chicken soup and cheese sauce. 200g.........$18.00

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation="bottom-to-top" css=".vc_custom_1447764903061{padding-right: 55px !important;padding-left: 55px !important;}"]

CRANBERRY BBQ CHICKEN

A very pretty chicken; you can use a whole chicken cut up, or pieces. I generally use Country Legs. 200g.........$10.00

[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image="53" img_size="full" alignment="center" css_animation="bottom-to-top" css=".vc_custom_1447336069150{margin-top: -2px !important;}"][vc_column_text css_animation="bottom-to-top" css=".vc_custom_1447765037241{margin-top: -2px !important;padding-right: 55px !important;padding-left: 55px !important;}"]

SLOPPY JOES

No green pepper in this recipe, so it's a hit with kids. We added this to the menu at a children's camp. 200g.........$19.00

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_single_image image="57" img_size="full" alignment="center" css_animation="right-to-left"][vc_single_image image="33" img_size="full" alignment="center" css_animation="right-to-left"][vc_column_text css_animation="right-to-left" css=".vc_custom_1447337061460{margin-top: -35px !important;}"]

FREE HOME DELIVERY

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation="right-to-left" css=".vc_custom_1447337137949{margin-top: -20px !important;padding-right: 50px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"]

LUNCH MENU SERVED EVERYDAY FROM 12:00 TO 15:00

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation="right-to-left" css=".vc_custom_1447337143136{margin-top: -20px !important;padding-right: 50px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"]

DINNER SERVED FROM 18:00 TO 21:00

[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image="59" img_size="full" alignment="center" css_animation="right-to-left" css=".vc_custom_1447337203299{margin-top: -11px !important;}"][/vc_column][/vc_row]
